      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this car in person\u2014it\u2019s an absolute gem! I've babied this ride since day one, and it\u2019s still in total mint condition, looking and smelling just like it did on the showroom floor. It drives like a dream and has been kept spotless inside and out. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is your lucky day! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
