    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. This specimen features the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine with its complex sequential twin-turbocharger system functioning flawlessly, delivering linear boost across the RPM range. The chassis retains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by an untouched four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for surgical turn-in precision. Meticulously preserved, the 'rat\u2019s nest' vacuum system is tight, and the apex seals show optimal compression. With pristine factory paint and an interior free of the typical plastics degradation, this is a rare, unmolested example for the serious purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
