    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly remarkable, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies the most discerning standards. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never been exposed to harsh weather or road salt. The exterior features a deep, mirror-finish paint depth, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks, and is protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the interior is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and all original factory protective films remain on the door sills. Every technological feature, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is in peak form with a fully documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, and the undercarriage is exceptionally clean. This is a rare, investment-grade example for a buyer who demands perfection without compromise. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
